name: Professionally Stretched Canvas Print 24"x24" (61cm x 61cm)
description:
WHY CHOOSE US?
We pride ourselves in giving you the highest quality prints in the market. We treat the printing of your own images like we are printing our own. In instances where you do not have your own image and you ask us to source art for you we do it legitimately  (paying all required royalties) and we reproduce it at a size that suits you.

* We DO NOT offer cheap materials, inks or media
* We only use the best brand name canvas
* We use inks lab tested to be fade resistant up to 200 years.   
* Our prints are water smudge resistant
* Our prints are scratch and abrasion resistant
